'''戴维·罗伯特·米切尔'''（David Robert Mitchell，{{bd|1974年||||catIdx=M}}）是一位[[美国电影|美国电影]]导演和编剧。主要作品有2010年的 ''The Myth of the American Sleepover''，以及2014年得到广泛好评的[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]《[[神秘追随|神秘追随]]》。<ref name="nyti_Indi">{{Cite web| title = Indie Horror Movie 'It Follows' Gets Wide Theater Release| last = Press| first = The Associated| work = New York Times| date = 27 March 2015| accessdate = 2015-03-28| url = http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/03/27/arts/ap-us-film-it-follows.html| archive-date = 2015-04-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150408100021/http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/03/27/arts/ap-us-film-it-follows.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="past_TheF">{{Cite web| title = The Feeling of Following: An Interview with David Robert Mitchell| author = Andy Crump| work = Paste Magazine| date = 2015-03-17| accessdate = 2015-03-28| url = http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2015/03/the-feeling-of-following-an-interview-with-david-r.html| archive-date = 2019-09-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190921060956/https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2015/03/the-feeling-of-following-an-interview-with-david-r.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

==生平==
